@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Login - copia el token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Define el token manualmente aquí tras hacer login
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjEsInJvbGUiOiJBRE1JTiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTc1MTQ4NiwiZXhwIjoxNzc1NzU4Njg2fQ.DwAQHwLwz_r_mY3bxtUg5LA1W_MHBdKWDVbz7PtYupc

### 3. Get my profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books

### 5. Get books con filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?genre=Misterio&page=1&limit=5

### 6. Get book by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1

### 7. Create book (necesita LIBRARIAN o ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isbn": "978-84-000-0001-1",
  "title": "Libro de prueba",
  "author": "Autor Test",
  "genre": "Ficción",
  "publishedYear": 2020,
  "copies": 3
}

### 8. Create loan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bookId": 1
}

### 9. My loans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Return loan
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/loans/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get reviews of book
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1/reviews

### 12. Create review (necesita haber devuelto el libro)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excelente libro"
}

### 13. Delete review
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}